.TP
\f[CR]\-\-no\-quotes\f[R]
Don\(cqt quote file names with spaces.
.TP
\f[CR]\-\-hyperlink=WHEN\f[R]
Display entries as hyperlinks
.PP
Valid settings are \(oq\f[CR]always\f[R]\(cq,
